WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.497 --> 00:00:08.060
"Feeling Is The Secret,"
by Neville Goddard.

00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:09.703
Read by Adam Hammond.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:13.720
In this volume, Neville has succeeded

00:00:13.720 --> 00:00:17.860
in describing how through our
imagination and our feelings

00:00:17.860 --> 00:00:22.300
we consciously or unconsciously
mold outer circumstance

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:24.860
in harmony with our inner nature.

00:00:24.860 --> 00:00:27.320
Here, he has given us a simple formula

00:00:27.320 --> 00:00:28.923
to realize our desires.

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:34.883
Originally published by GMJ
Publishing Company in 1944.

00:00:35.910 --> 00:00:39.430
This recording is a production
of the Master Key Society.

00:00:39.430 --> 00:00:43.473
Copyright 2021 Master Key Society.

00:00:44.727 --> 00:00:49.727
"Of making many books, there
is no end," Ecclesiastes 12:12.

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:57.180
He that would perfect himself
in any art whatsoever,

00:00:57.180 --> 00:01:00.320
let him betake himself to
the reading of some sure

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:04.610
and certain work upon
his art many times over.

00:01:04.610 --> 00:01:07.451
For to read many books upon your art

00:01:07.451 --> 00:01:11.873
produceth confusion rather
than learning, old saying.

00:01:15.810 --> 00:01:16.643
Foreword.

00:01:17.540 --> 00:01:18.690
This book is concerned

00:01:18.690 --> 00:01:21.910
with the art of realizing your desire.

00:01:21.910 --> 00:01:24.510
It gives you an account
of the mechanism used

00:01:24.510 --> 00:01:26.460
in the production of the visible world.

00:01:27.350 --> 00:01:30.033
It is a small book, but not slight.

00:01:30.890 --> 00:01:32.650
There is a treasure in it,

00:01:32.650 --> 00:01:36.273
a clearly defined road to the
realization of your dreams.

00:01:37.550 --> 00:01:40.110
Were it possible to carry
conviction to another

00:01:40.110 --> 00:01:43.640
by means of reasoned arguments
and detailed instances,

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:45.983
this book would be many times its size.

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:49.480
It is seldom possible, however, to do so

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:52.410
by means of written
statements or arguments

00:01:52.410 --> 00:01:54.460
since to the suspended judgment

00:01:54.460 --> 00:01:56.640
it always seems plausible to say that

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:59.280
the author was dishonest or diluted,

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:02.193
and therefore his evidence was tainted.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:04.600
Consequently,

00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:08.520
I have purposely omitted all
arguments and testimonials

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:10.980
and simply challenge
the open-minded reader

00:02:10.980 --> 00:02:13.500
to practice the law of consciousness

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:15.023
as revealed in this book.

00:02:15.910 --> 00:02:19.010
Personal success will
prove far more convincing

00:02:19.010 --> 00:02:22.373
than all the books that could
be written on the subject.

00:02:23.490 --> 00:02:24.323
Neville

00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:27.883
Chapter one.

00:02:28.930 --> 00:02:30.793
Law and Its Operation.

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:35.360
The world and all within it,

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:38.393
is man's conditioned
consciousness objectified.

00:02:39.600 --> 00:02:40.970
Consciousness is the cause

00:02:40.970 --> 00:02:44.090
as well as the substance
of the entire world.

00:02:44.090 --> 00:02:47.400
So it is to consciousness
that we must turn

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:49.803
if we would discover
the secret of creation.

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:52.760
Knowledge of the law of consciousness

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:54.710
and the method of operating this law

00:02:54.710 --> 00:02:57.763
will enable you to accomplish
all you desire in life.

00:02:58.690 --> 00:03:01.150
Armed with a working
knowledge of this law,

00:03:01.150 --> 00:03:04.133
you can build and maintain an ideal world.

00:03:05.610 --> 00:03:09.060
Consciousness is the one and only reality,

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:11.713
not figuratively but actually.

00:03:12.660 --> 00:03:15.230
This reality may for the sake of clarity,

00:03:15.230 --> 00:03:19.300
be likened unto a stream, which
is divided into two parts,

00:03:19.300 --> 00:03:21.343
the conscious and the subconscious.

00:03:22.180 --> 00:03:25.490
In order to intelligently
operate the law of consciousness,

00:03:25.490 --> 00:03:27.860
it is necessary to
understand the relationship

00:03:27.860 --> 00:03:30.010
between the conscious
and the subconscious.

00:03:30.850 --> 00:03:33.890
The conscious is personal and selective,

00:03:33.890 --> 00:03:37.183
the subconscious is
impersonal and non-selective.

00:03:38.190 --> 00:03:40.410
The conscious is the realm of effect,

00:03:40.410 --> 00:03:43.063
the subconscious is the realm of cause.

00:03:43.900 --> 00:03:45.260
These two aspects

00:03:45.260 --> 00:03:48.233
are the male and female
divisions of consciousness.

00:03:49.130 --> 00:03:52.563
The conscious is male, the
subconscious is female.

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:55.820
The conscious generates ideas

00:03:55.820 --> 00:03:59.110
and impresses these ideas
on the subconscious.

00:03:59.110 --> 00:04:01.380
The subconscious receives ideas

00:04:01.380 --> 00:04:03.983
and gives form and expression to them.

00:04:05.050 --> 00:04:07.840
By this law, first conceiving an idea

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:11.600
and then impressing the idea
conceived on the subconscious,

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:14.520
all things evolve out of consciousness.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:17.560
And without this sequence
there is not anything made

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:18.720
that is made.

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:21.460
The conscious impresses the subconscious

00:04:21.460 --> 00:04:23.730
while the subconscious expresses

00:04:23.730 --> 00:04:25.723
all that is impressed upon it.

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:29.650
The subconscious does not originate ideas,

00:04:29.650 --> 00:04:33.020
but accepts as true those
which the conscious mind

00:04:33.020 --> 00:04:37.920
feels to be true and in a
way known only to itself

00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:40.363
objectifies the accepted ideas.

00:04:41.380 --> 00:04:44.410
Therefore, through his
power to imagine and feel

00:04:44.410 --> 00:04:47.980
and his freedom to choose
the idea he will entertain,

00:04:47.980 --> 00:04:50.443
man has control over creation.

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:53.900
Control of the subconscious
is accomplished

00:04:53.900 --> 00:04:56.713
through control of your
ideas and feelings.

00:04:58.010 --> 00:05:01.020
The mechanism of creation
is hidden in the very depth

00:05:01.020 --> 00:05:05.413
of the subconscious, the female
aspect or womb of creation.

00:05:06.400 --> 00:05:08.620
The subconscious transcends reason

00:05:08.620 --> 00:05:11.480
and is independent of induction.

00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:15.320
It contemplates a feeling as
a fact existing within itself

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:18.893
and on this assumption proceeds
to give expression to it.

00:05:20.020 --> 00:05:22.370
The creative process begins with an idea

00:05:22.370 --> 00:05:25.760
and its cycle runs its course as a feeling

00:05:25.760 --> 00:05:28.403
and ends in a volition to act.

00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:32.160
Ideas are impressed on the subconscious

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:33.753
through the medium of feeling.

00:05:34.700 --> 00:05:37.280
No idea can be impressed
on the subconscious

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:40.060
until it is felt, but once felt,

00:05:40.060 --> 00:05:44.323
be it good, bad or indifferent,
it must be expressed.

00:05:45.220 --> 00:05:48.000
Feeling is the one and only medium

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:51.520
through which ideas are
conveyed to the subconscious.

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:54.820
Therefore, the man who does
not control his feeling

00:05:54.820 --> 00:05:58.693
may easily impress the subconscious
with undesirable states.

00:05:59.570 --> 00:06:00.850
By control of feeling

00:06:00.850 --> 00:06:04.230
is not meant restraint or
suppression of your feeling,

00:06:04.230 --> 00:06:08.470
but rather the disciplining of
self to imagine and entertain

00:06:08.470 --> 00:06:12.033
only such feeling as
contributes to your happiness.

00:06:13.270 --> 00:06:15.140
Control of your feeling is all important

00:06:15.140 --> 00:06:17.400
to a full and happy life.

00:06:17.400 --> 00:06:20.740
Never entertain an undesirable feeling

00:06:20.740 --> 00:06:24.993
nor think sympathetically about
wrong in any shape or form.

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:30.000
Do not dwell on the imperfection
of yourself or others.

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:32.410
To do so is to impress the subconscious

00:06:32.410 --> 00:06:34.350
with these limitations.

00:06:34.350 --> 00:06:37.170
What you do not want done unto you

00:06:37.170 --> 00:06:41.630
do not feel that it is
done unto you or another.

00:06:41.630 --> 00:06:45.860
This is the whole law of
a full and happy life.

00:06:45.860 --> 00:06:47.573
Everything else is commentary.

00:06:49.430 --> 00:06:52.230
Every feeling makes a
subconscious impression

00:06:52.230 --> 00:06:54.030
and unless it is counteracted

00:06:54.030 --> 00:06:57.050
by a more powerful feeling
of an opposite nature

00:06:57.050 --> 00:06:58.503
must be expressed.

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:02.273
The dominant of two feelings
is the one expressed.

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:08.160
I am healthy is a stronger
feeling than I will be healthy.

00:07:09.470 --> 00:07:13.903
To feel I will be is to confess I am not.

00:07:14.860 --> 00:07:18.260
I am is stronger than I am not.

00:07:18.260 --> 00:07:21.110
What you feel you are always dominates

00:07:21.110 --> 00:07:23.870
what you feel you would like to be,

00:07:23.870 --> 00:07:28.440
therefore to be realized the
wish must be felt as a state

00:07:28.440 --> 00:07:31.763
that is rather than a state that is not.

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:35.690
Sensation proceeds manifestation

00:07:35.690 --> 00:07:38.923
and is the foundation upon
which all manifestation rests.

00:07:40.030 --> 00:07:42.740
Be careful of your moods and feelings,

00:07:42.740 --> 00:07:44.530
for there is an unbroken connection

00:07:44.530 --> 00:07:46.903
between your feelings
and your visible world.

00:07:48.170 --> 00:07:50.140
Your body is an emotional filter

00:07:50.140 --> 00:07:53.623
and bears the unmistakable marks
of your prevalent emotions.

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:58.280
Emotional disturbances,
especially suppressed emotions

00:07:58.280 --> 00:08:00.213
are the causes of all disease.

00:08:01.050 --> 00:08:03.240
To feel intensely about a wrong

00:08:03.240 --> 00:08:05.870
without voicing or expressing that feeling

00:08:05.870 --> 00:08:08.040
is the beginning of disease,

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:11.723
dis-ease in both body and environment.

00:08:12.840 --> 00:08:15.790
Do not entertain the
feeling of regret or failure

00:08:15.790 --> 00:08:19.870
for frustration or detachment
from your objective results

00:08:19.870 --> 00:08:20.703
in disease.

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:26.173
Think feelingly only of the
state you desire to realize.

00:08:27.060 --> 00:08:29.370
Feeling the reality of the state sought

00:08:29.370 --> 00:08:31.810
and living and acting on that conviction

00:08:31.810 --> 00:08:34.553
is the way of all seeming miracles.

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:38.150
All changes of expression
are brought about

00:08:38.150 --> 00:08:40.570
through a change of feeling.

00:08:40.570 --> 00:08:43.373
A change of feeling is
a change of destiny.

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:47.860
All creation occurs in the
domain of the subconscious.

00:08:47.860 --> 00:08:51.600
What you must acquire then
is a reflective control

00:08:51.600 --> 00:08:54.170
of the operation of the subconscious,

00:08:54.170 --> 00:08:58.303
that is control of your
ideas and feelings.

00:08:59.640 --> 00:09:02.290
Chance or accident is not responsible

00:09:02.290 --> 00:09:06.470
for the things that happen to
you nor is predestined fate

00:09:06.470 --> 00:09:09.123
the author of your fortune or misfortune.

00:09:10.100 --> 00:09:12.340
Your subconscious impressions

00:09:12.340 --> 00:09:14.463
determine the conditions of your world.

00:09:15.380 --> 00:09:17.460
The subconscious is not selective,

00:09:17.460 --> 00:09:20.973
it is impersonal and no
respecter of persons.

00:09:22.350 --> 00:09:24.400
The subconscious is not concerned

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:27.300
with the truth or falsity of your feeling.

00:09:27.300 --> 00:09:30.653
It always accepts as true
that what you feel to be true.

00:09:31.570 --> 00:09:34.170
Feeling is the ascent of the subconscious

00:09:34.170 --> 00:09:37.790
to the truth of that which
is declared to be true.

00:09:37.790 --> 00:09:40.810
Because of this quality
of the subconscious,

00:09:40.810 --> 00:09:43.033
there was nothing impossible to man.

00:09:44.010 --> 00:09:47.630
Whatever the mind of man can
conceive and feel as true,

00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:50.753
the subconscious can and must objectify.

00:09:51.660 --> 00:09:54.040
Your feelings create the pattern

00:09:54.040 --> 00:09:56.300
from which your world is fashioned

00:09:56.300 --> 00:09:59.233
and a change of feeling
is a change of pattern.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:02.980
The subconscious never fails to express

00:10:02.980 --> 00:10:05.750
that which has been impressed upon it.

00:10:05.750 --> 00:10:07.730
The moment it receives an impression,

00:10:07.730 --> 00:10:10.613
it begins to work out the
ways of its expression.

00:10:11.490 --> 00:10:15.210
It accepts the feeling
impressed upon it, your feeling,

00:10:15.210 --> 00:10:20.120
as a fact, existing within
itself and immediately sets about

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:23.400
to produce in the outer or objective world

00:10:23.400 --> 00:10:25.863
the exact likeness of that feeling.

00:10:27.030 --> 00:10:31.710
The subconscious never alters
the accepted beliefs of man

00:10:31.710 --> 00:10:34.680
it out-pictures them to the last detail

00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:36.773
whether or not they are beneficial.

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:41.520
To impress the subconscious
with the desirable state,

00:10:41.520 --> 00:10:44.340
you must assume the
feeling that would be yours

00:10:44.340 --> 00:10:46.573
had you already realized your wish.

00:10:47.580 --> 00:10:49.280
In defining your objective,

00:10:49.280 --> 00:10:52.383
you must be concerned only
with the objective itself.

00:10:53.270 --> 00:10:56.480
The manner of expression or
the difficulties involved

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:58.623
are not to be considered by you.

00:10:59.610 --> 00:11:01.820
To think feelingly on any state

00:11:01.820 --> 00:11:04.590
impresses it on the subconscious.

00:11:04.590 --> 00:11:08.630
Therefore, if you dwell on
difficulties, barriers, or delay

00:11:08.630 --> 00:11:11.980
the subconscious by its
very non-selective nature

00:11:11.980 --> 00:11:14.980
accepts the feeling of
difficulties and obstacles

00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:18.330
as your request and
proceeds to produce them

00:11:18.330 --> 00:11:19.623
in your outer world.

00:11:21.500 --> 00:11:24.460
The subconscious is the womb of creation.

00:11:24.460 --> 00:11:26.900
It receives the idea unto itself

00:11:26.900 --> 00:11:29.090
through the feelings of man.

00:11:29.090 --> 00:11:31.500
It never changes the idea received,

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:33.093
but always gives it form.

00:11:33.930 --> 00:11:36.247
Hence the subconscious
out-pictures the idea

00:11:36.247 --> 00:11:39.043
and the image and likeness
of the feeling received.

00:11:39.880 --> 00:11:42.840
To feel a state as hopeless or impossible

00:11:42.840 --> 00:11:46.223
is to impress the subconscious
with the idea of failure.

00:11:47.860 --> 00:11:51.040
Although the subconscious
faithfully serves man,

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:53.390
it must not be inferred that the relation

00:11:53.390 --> 00:11:57.283
is that of a servant to a master
as was anciently conceived.

00:11:58.460 --> 00:12:02.720
The ancient prophets called it
the slave and servant of man.

00:12:02.720 --> 00:12:06.787
St. Paul personified
it as a woman and said,

00:12:06.787 --> 00:12:10.747
"The woman should be subject
to man in everything."

00:12:12.430 --> 00:12:14.090
The subconscious does serve man

00:12:14.090 --> 00:12:16.770
and faithfully gives form to his feelings.

00:12:16.770 --> 00:12:19.670
However, the subconscious
has a distinct distaste

00:12:19.670 --> 00:12:22.860
for compulsion and responds to persuasion

00:12:22.860 --> 00:12:24.890
rather than to command.

00:12:24.890 --> 00:12:27.720
Consequently, it
resembles the beloved wife

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:29.073
more than the servant.

00:12:30.490 --> 00:12:34.970
The husband is head of
the wife, Ephesians 5,

00:12:34.970 --> 00:12:36.900
may not be true of man and woman

00:12:36.900 --> 00:12:38.920
in their earthly relationship,

00:12:38.920 --> 00:12:41.900
but it is true of the
conscious and the subconscious

00:12:41.900 --> 00:12:44.913
or the male and female
aspects of consciousness.

00:12:45.950 --> 00:12:48.817
The mystery to which Paul
referred when he wrote,

00:12:48.817 --> 00:12:50.657
"This is a great mystery.

00:12:50.657 --> 00:12:53.857
"He that loveth his wife loveth himself

00:12:53.857 --> 00:12:56.950
"and they two shall be one flesh,"

00:12:56.950 --> 00:12:59.003
is simply the mystery of consciousness.

00:13:00.370 --> 00:13:03.510
Consciousness is really one and undivided

00:13:03.510 --> 00:13:06.963
but for creation's sake, it
appears to be divided into two.

00:13:08.330 --> 00:13:12.870
The conscious, objective or
male aspect truly is the head

00:13:12.870 --> 00:13:17.460
and dominates the subconscious,
subjective or female aspect.

00:13:17.460 --> 00:13:20.460
However, this leadership
is not that of the tyrant,

00:13:20.460 --> 00:13:22.220
but of the lover.

00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:25.020
So by assuming the feeling
that would be yours

00:13:25.020 --> 00:13:27.940
were you already in
possession of your objective,

00:13:27.940 --> 00:13:29.900
the subconscious is moved to build

00:13:29.900 --> 00:13:32.083
the exact likeness of your assumption.

00:13:33.190 --> 00:13:35.890
Your desires are not
subconsciously accepted

00:13:35.890 --> 00:13:39.060
until you assume the
feeling of their reality,

00:13:39.060 --> 00:13:43.410
for only through feeling is an
idea subconsciously accepted

00:13:43.410 --> 00:13:45.890
and only through this
subconscious acceptance

00:13:45.890 --> 00:13:47.343
is it ever expressed.

00:13:48.940 --> 00:13:52.270
It is easier to ascribe your
feeling to events in the world

00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:54.280
than to admit that the
conditions of the world

00:13:54.280 --> 00:13:55.523
reflect your feeling.

00:13:56.360 --> 00:13:58.250
However, it is eternally true

00:13:58.250 --> 00:14:00.863
that the outside mirrors the inside,

00:14:01.737 --> 00:14:04.197
"As within so without."

00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:07.240
A man can receive nothing,

00:14:07.240 --> 00:14:10.010
unless it is given him from heaven.

00:14:10.010 --> 00:14:13.393
And the kingdom of heaven is within you.

00:14:15.150 --> 00:14:19.060
Nothing comes from without,
all things come from within,

00:14:19.060 --> 00:14:21.180
from the subconscious.

00:14:21.180 --> 00:14:23.010
It is impossible for you to see

00:14:23.010 --> 00:14:26.000
other than the contents
of your consciousness.

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:28.630
Your world in its every detail

00:14:28.630 --> 00:14:30.883
is your consciousness objectified.

00:14:32.280 --> 00:14:36.220
Objective states bear witness
of subconscious impressions.

00:14:36.220 --> 00:14:39.943
A change of impression results
in a change of expression.

00:14:41.890 --> 00:14:43.760
The subconscious accepts as true

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:45.740
that which you feel as true

00:14:45.740 --> 00:14:47.120
and because creation

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:49.570
is the result of subconscious impressions,

00:14:49.570 --> 00:14:53.830
you by your feeling determine creation.

00:14:53.830 --> 00:14:57.540
You are already that which you want to be

00:14:57.540 --> 00:14:59.280
and your refusal to believe this

00:14:59.280 --> 00:15:01.563
is the only reason you do not see it.

00:15:02.710 --> 00:15:04.330
To seek on the outside for that

00:15:04.330 --> 00:15:08.140
which you do not feel you
are is to seek in vain,

00:15:08.140 --> 00:15:11.410
for we never find that which we want,

00:15:11.410 --> 00:15:14.163
we find only that which we are.

00:15:15.070 --> 00:15:19.060
In short, you express and have only that

00:15:19.060 --> 00:15:21.593
which you are conscious
of being or possessing.

00:15:22.767 --> 00:15:25.127
"To him that hath it is given."

00:15:26.320 --> 00:15:28.100
Denying the evidence of the senses

00:15:28.100 --> 00:15:30.980
and appropriating the
feeling of the wish fulfilled

00:15:30.980 --> 00:15:34.203
is the way to the
realization of your desire.

00:15:35.430 --> 00:15:38.670
Mastery of self control of
your thoughts and feelings

00:15:38.670 --> 00:15:40.413
is your highest achievement.

00:15:41.320 --> 00:15:44.670
However, until perfect
self control is attained,

00:15:44.670 --> 00:15:47.230
so that in spite of appearances,

00:15:47.230 --> 00:15:52.230
you feel all that you want
to feel use sleep and prayer

00:15:52.390 --> 00:15:56.020
to aid you in realizing
your desired states.

00:15:56.020 --> 00:15:59.563
These are the two gateways
into the subconscious.

00:16:01.400 --> 00:16:02.383
Chapter two.

00:16:03.290 --> 00:16:04.123
Sleep.

00:16:06.260 --> 00:16:11.050
Sleep, the life that occupies
one third of our stay on earth

00:16:11.050 --> 00:16:13.923
is the natural door into the subconscious.

00:16:14.860 --> 00:16:17.553
So it is with sleep that
we are now concerned.

00:16:18.580 --> 00:16:20.580
The conscious two-thirds
of our life on earth

00:16:20.580 --> 00:16:24.000
is measured by the degree
of attention we give sleep.

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:27.590
Our understanding of and delight
in what sleep has to bestow

00:16:27.590 --> 00:16:31.330
will cause us night after
night to set out for it

00:16:31.330 --> 00:16:34.293
as though we were keeping
an appointment with a lover.

00:16:35.817 --> 00:16:38.137
"In a dream, in a vision of the night,

00:16:38.137 --> 00:16:40.517
"when deep sleep falleth upon men

00:16:40.517 --> 00:16:43.047
"in slumbering upon the bed,

00:16:43.047 --> 00:16:45.587
"then he openeth the ears of men

00:16:45.587 --> 00:16:50.483
"and sealeth their instruction," Job 33.

00:16:51.930 --> 00:16:55.510
It is in sleep and in
prayer, a state akin to sleep

00:16:55.510 --> 00:16:58.780
that man enters the subconscious
to make his impressions

00:16:58.780 --> 00:17:01.320
and receive his instructions.

00:17:01.320 --> 00:17:04.190
In these states, the
conscious and subconscious

00:17:04.190 --> 00:17:09.113
are creatively joined, the male
and female become one flesh.

00:17:10.290 --> 00:17:13.560
Sleep is the time when
the male or conscious mind

00:17:13.560 --> 00:17:16.320
turns from the world of
sense to seek its lover

00:17:16.320 --> 00:17:17.713
or subconscious self.

00:17:18.790 --> 00:17:21.160
The subconscious, unlike
the woman of the world

00:17:21.160 --> 00:17:23.680
who marries her husband to change him

00:17:23.680 --> 00:17:27.470
has no desire to change
the conscious waking state,

00:17:27.470 --> 00:17:32.090
but loves it as it is and
faithfully reproduces its likeness

00:17:32.090 --> 00:17:33.763
in the outer world of form.

00:17:34.820 --> 00:17:36.850
The conditions and events of your life

00:17:36.850 --> 00:17:38.910
are your children formed from the molds

00:17:38.910 --> 00:17:42.400
of your subconscious impressions in sleep.

00:17:42.400 --> 00:17:44.390
They are made in the image and likeness

00:17:44.390 --> 00:17:47.450
of your innermost feeling
that they may reveal you

00:17:47.450 --> 00:17:48.333
to yourself.

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:51.933
As in heaven so on earth.

00:17:52.810 --> 00:17:55.053
As in the subconscious so on earth.

00:17:55.970 --> 00:17:59.020
Whatever you have in
consciousness as you go to sleep

00:17:59.020 --> 00:18:00.730
is the measure of your expression

00:18:00.730 --> 00:18:03.080
in the waking two thirds
of your life on earth.

00:18:03.930 --> 00:18:06.820
Nothing stops you from
realizing your objective

00:18:06.820 --> 00:18:10.050
save your failure to feel
that you are already that

00:18:10.050 --> 00:18:11.770
which you wish to be

00:18:11.770 --> 00:18:15.313
or that you are already in
possession of the thing sought.

00:18:16.340 --> 00:18:19.760
Your subconscious gives
form to your desires

00:18:19.760 --> 00:18:22.463
only when you feel your wish fulfilled.

00:18:24.120 --> 00:18:25.510
The unconsciousness of sleep

00:18:25.510 --> 00:18:28.000
is the normal state of the subconscious

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:31.070
because all things come
from within yourself

00:18:31.070 --> 00:18:35.250
and your conception of yourself
determines that which comes.

00:18:35.250 --> 00:18:37.760
You should always feel the wish fulfilled

00:18:37.760 --> 00:18:40.260
before you drop off to sleep.

00:18:40.260 --> 00:18:42.670
You never draw out of the deep of yourself

00:18:42.670 --> 00:18:46.770
that what you want, you
always draw that which you are

00:18:46.770 --> 00:18:50.490
and you are that which
you feel yourself to be

00:18:50.490 --> 00:18:53.863
as well as that which you
feel as true of others.

00:18:55.170 --> 00:18:58.210
To be realized then, the
wish must be resolved

00:18:58.210 --> 00:19:02.430
into the feeling of being
or having or witnessing

00:19:02.430 --> 00:19:03.553
the state sought.

00:19:05.130 --> 00:19:06.700
This is accomplished by assuming

00:19:06.700 --> 00:19:08.400
the feeling of the wish fulfilled.

00:19:09.510 --> 00:19:12.227
The feeling which comes in
response to the question,

00:19:12.227 --> 00:19:15.500
"How would I feel were my wish realized,"

00:19:15.500 --> 00:19:17.490
is the feeling which should monopolize

00:19:17.490 --> 00:19:21.073
and immobilize your attention
as you relax into sleep.

00:19:21.970 --> 00:19:25.350
You must be in the
consciousness of being or having

00:19:25.350 --> 00:19:28.050
that which you want to be or to have

00:19:28.050 --> 00:19:29.833
before you drop off to sleep.

00:19:31.640 --> 00:19:35.320
Once asleep, man has no freedom of choice.

00:19:35.320 --> 00:19:37.270
His entire slumber is dominated

00:19:37.270 --> 00:19:39.563
by his last waking concept of self.

00:19:40.400 --> 00:19:42.670
It follows therefore that
he should always assume

00:19:42.670 --> 00:19:45.160
the feeling of accomplishment
and satisfaction

00:19:45.160 --> 00:19:47.053
before he retires in sleep.

00:19:47.890 --> 00:19:51.280
Come before me with
singing and thanksgiving.

00:19:51.280 --> 00:19:53.460
Enter into his gates with thanksgiving

00:19:53.460 --> 00:19:55.353
and into his courts with praise.

00:19:56.470 --> 00:19:58.670
Your mood prior to sleep

00:19:58.670 --> 00:20:00.700
defines your state of consciousness

00:20:00.700 --> 00:20:04.380
as you enter into the presence
of your everlasting lover,

00:20:04.380 --> 00:20:06.290
the subconscious.

00:20:06.290 --> 00:20:09.950
She sees you exactly as
you feel yourself to be.

00:20:09.950 --> 00:20:11.780
If as you prepare for sleep,

00:20:11.780 --> 00:20:14.950
you assume and maintain the
consciousness of success

00:20:14.950 --> 00:20:19.633
by feeling I am successful,
you must be successful.

00:20:21.080 --> 00:20:22.210
Lie flat on your back

00:20:22.210 --> 00:20:24.470
with your head on a level with your body,

00:20:24.470 --> 00:20:27.920
feel as you would were you
in possession of your wish

00:20:27.920 --> 00:20:30.323
and quietly relax into unconsciousness.

00:20:32.260 --> 00:20:35.403
He that keepeth Israel shall
neither slumber nor sleep.

00:20:36.330 --> 00:20:39.733
Nevertheless, he giveth his beloved sleep.

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:43.730
The subconscious never sleeps.

00:20:43.730 --> 00:20:46.880
Sleep is the door through
which the conscious waking mind

00:20:46.880 --> 00:20:50.763
passes to be creatively
joined to the subconscious.

00:20:51.800 --> 00:20:54.370
Sleep conceals the creative act

00:20:54.370 --> 00:20:56.583
while the objective world reveals it.

00:20:57.580 --> 00:21:00.500
In sleep, man impresses the subconscious

00:21:00.500 --> 00:21:02.183
with his conception of himself.

00:21:03.340 --> 00:21:05.190
What more beautiful description

00:21:05.190 --> 00:21:09.210
of this romance of the conscious
and subconscious is there

00:21:09.210 --> 00:21:11.763
than that told in the song of Solomon.

00:21:12.847 --> 00:21:17.637
"By night on my bed, I sought
him whom my soul loveth.

00:21:17.637 --> 00:21:21.597
"I found him whom my soul loveth.

00:21:21.597 --> 00:21:24.807
"I held him and I would not let him go

00:21:24.807 --> 00:21:27.827
"until I had brought him
into my mother's house

00:21:27.827 --> 00:21:30.847
"and into the chamber of
her that conceived me."

00:21:32.840 --> 00:21:35.530
Preparing to sleep you feel yourself

00:21:35.530 --> 00:21:37.920
into the state of the answered wish

00:21:37.920 --> 00:21:39.923
and then relax into unconsciousness.

00:21:40.950 --> 00:21:44.053
Your realized wish is he whom you seek.

00:21:45.100 --> 00:21:46.700
By night on your bed

00:21:46.700 --> 00:21:49.040
you seek the feeling of the wish fulfilled

00:21:49.040 --> 00:21:51.460
that you may take it
with you into the chamber

00:21:51.460 --> 00:21:55.640
of her that conceived you,
into sleep or the subconscious

00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:58.350
which gave you form that this wish

00:21:58.350 --> 00:22:00.263
also may be given expression.

00:22:01.270 --> 00:22:04.280
This is the way to discover
and conduct your wishes

00:22:04.280 --> 00:22:06.100
into the subconscious.

00:22:06.100 --> 00:22:09.310
Feel yourself in the
state of the realized wish

00:22:09.310 --> 00:22:11.363
and quietly drop off to sleep.

00:22:12.840 --> 00:22:15.970
Night after night, you should
assume the feeling of being,

00:22:15.970 --> 00:22:20.270
having, and witnessing that
which you seek to be possessed

00:22:20.270 --> 00:22:21.733
and see manifested.

00:22:22.720 --> 00:22:26.620
Never go to sleep feeling
discouraged or dissatisfied.

00:22:26.620 --> 00:22:29.680
Never sleep in the
consciousness of failure.

00:22:29.680 --> 00:22:32.850
Your subconscious whose
natural state is sleep,

00:22:32.850 --> 00:22:36.510
sees you as you believe yourself to be,

00:22:36.510 --> 00:22:40.140
and whether it be good,
bad, or indifferent,

00:22:40.140 --> 00:22:43.013
the subconscious will
faithfully embody your belief.

00:22:44.210 --> 00:22:47.390
As you feel, so do you impress her.

00:22:47.390 --> 00:22:51.770
And she the perfect lover
gives form to these impressions

00:22:51.770 --> 00:22:54.923
and out-pictures them as
the children of her beloved.

00:22:56.850 --> 00:22:59.060
Thou art all fair, my love,

00:22:59.060 --> 00:23:01.360
there is no spot in thee.

00:23:01.360 --> 00:23:03.340
Is the attitude of mind to adopt

00:23:03.340 --> 00:23:04.993
before dropping off to sleep.

00:23:06.100 --> 00:23:08.840
Disregard appearances
and feel that things are

00:23:08.840 --> 00:23:12.760
as you wish them to be
for he calleth things

00:23:12.760 --> 00:23:15.290
that are not seen as though they were

00:23:15.290 --> 00:23:17.453
and the unseen becomes seen.

00:23:18.820 --> 00:23:21.350
To assume the feeling of satisfaction

00:23:21.350 --> 00:23:23.170
is to call conditions into being

00:23:23.170 --> 00:23:25.053
which will mirror satisfaction.

00:23:26.100 --> 00:23:28.913
Signs follow, they do not precede.

00:23:30.040 --> 00:23:32.840
Proof that you are will
follow the consciousness

00:23:32.840 --> 00:23:34.360
that you are,

00:23:34.360 --> 00:23:35.713
it will not precede it.

00:23:37.010 --> 00:23:42.010
You are an eternal dreamer
dreaming non-internal dreams.

00:23:42.040 --> 00:23:43.270
Your dreams take form

00:23:43.270 --> 00:23:46.330
as you assume the
feeling of their reality.

00:23:46.330 --> 00:23:48.980
Do not limit yourself to the past.

00:23:48.980 --> 00:23:51.970
Knowing that nothing is
impossible to consciousness,

00:23:51.970 --> 00:23:56.053
begin to imagine states beyond
the experiences of the past.

00:23:56.980 --> 00:24:00.473
Whatever the mind of man can
imagine, man can realize.

00:24:01.350 --> 00:24:06.350
All objective visible
states were first subjective

00:24:06.970 --> 00:24:09.070
invisible states,

00:24:09.070 --> 00:24:10.910
and you called them into visible

00:24:10.910 --> 00:24:13.593
by assuming the feeling of their reality.

00:24:14.470 --> 00:24:16.700
The creative process is first imagining

00:24:16.700 --> 00:24:19.430
and then believing the state imagined.

00:24:19.430 --> 00:24:22.973
Always imagine and expect the best.

00:24:25.040 --> 00:24:26.730
The world cannot change

00:24:26.730 --> 00:24:29.800
until you change your conception of it.

00:24:29.800 --> 00:24:31.493
As within so without.

00:24:32.550 --> 00:24:34.130
Nations as well as people

00:24:34.130 --> 00:24:36.443
are only what you believe them to be.

00:24:37.350 --> 00:24:40.410
No matter what the problem
is, no matter where it is,

00:24:40.410 --> 00:24:42.980
no matter whom it concerns

00:24:42.980 --> 00:24:45.460
you have no one to change but yourself

00:24:46.520 --> 00:24:49.380
and you have neither opponent nor helper

00:24:49.380 --> 00:24:52.363
in bringing about the
change within yourself.

00:24:53.360 --> 00:24:57.100
You have nothing to do but
convince yourself of the truth

00:24:57.100 --> 00:25:00.003
of that which you desire
to see manifested.

00:25:01.240 --> 00:25:03.320
As soon as you succeed
in convincing yourself

00:25:03.320 --> 00:25:05.580
of the reality of the state sought,

00:25:05.580 --> 00:25:08.743
results follow to confirm
your fixed belief.

00:25:09.610 --> 00:25:12.550
You never suggest to another
the state which you desire

00:25:12.550 --> 00:25:14.730
to see him express.

00:25:14.730 --> 00:25:18.320
Instead, you convince
yourself that he is already

00:25:18.320 --> 00:25:20.403
that which you desire him to be.

00:25:22.160 --> 00:25:24.530
Realization of your wish is accomplished

00:25:24.530 --> 00:25:26.883
by assuming the feeling
of the wish fulfilled.

00:25:27.740 --> 00:25:31.220
You cannot fail unless you
fail to convince yourself

00:25:31.220 --> 00:25:32.913
of the reality of your wish.

00:25:33.940 --> 00:25:37.920
A change of belief is confirmed
by a change of expression.

00:25:37.920 --> 00:25:40.280
Every night as you drop off to sleep,

00:25:40.280 --> 00:25:42.800
feel satisfied and spotless

00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:46.277
for your subjective lover
always forms the objective world

00:25:46.277 --> 00:25:49.910
and the image and likeness
of your conception of it,

00:25:49.910 --> 00:25:52.403
the conception defined by your feeling.

00:25:53.720 --> 00:25:56.060
The waking two-thirds
of your life on earth

00:25:56.060 --> 00:25:58.630
ever corroborates or bears witness

00:25:58.630 --> 00:26:00.903
to your subconscious impressions.

00:26:01.790 --> 00:26:04.730
The actions and events
of the day are effects,

00:26:04.730 --> 00:26:06.560
they are not causes.

00:26:06.560 --> 00:26:08.803
Free will is only freedom of choice.

00:26:09.820 --> 00:26:12.810
Choose ye this day whom ye shall serve

00:26:12.810 --> 00:26:17.260
is your freedom to choose
the kind of mood you assume,

00:26:17.260 --> 00:26:19.000
but the expression of the mood

00:26:19.000 --> 00:26:21.233
is the secret of the subconscious.

00:26:22.110 --> 00:26:24.060
The subconscious receives impressions

00:26:24.060 --> 00:26:26.350
only through the feelings of man

00:26:26.350 --> 00:26:29.310
and in a way known only to itself

00:26:29.310 --> 00:26:33.010
gives these impressions
form and expression.

00:26:33.010 --> 00:26:34.880
The actions of man are determined

00:26:34.880 --> 00:26:37.410
by his subconscious impressions.

00:26:37.410 --> 00:26:41.790
His illusion of free will, his
belief and freedom of action

00:26:41.790 --> 00:26:44.463
is but ignorance of the
causes which make him act.

00:26:45.530 --> 00:26:49.510
He thinks himself free because
he has forgotten the link

00:26:49.510 --> 00:26:51.853
between himself and the event.

00:26:53.680 --> 00:26:56.520
Man awake is under compulsion to express

00:26:56.520 --> 00:26:58.223
his subconscious impressions.

00:26:59.080 --> 00:27:01.970
If in the past he unwisely
impressed himself,

00:27:01.970 --> 00:27:05.180
then let him begin to change
his thought and feeling

00:27:05.180 --> 00:27:09.273
for only as he does so
will he change his world.

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:13.120
Do not waste one moment in regret

00:27:13.120 --> 00:27:15.800
for to think feelingly of
the mistakes of the past

00:27:15.800 --> 00:27:17.393
is to reinfect yourself.

00:27:18.660 --> 00:27:20.683
Let the dead bury the dead.

00:27:21.600 --> 00:27:22.800
Turn from appearances

00:27:22.800 --> 00:27:25.200
and assume the feeling that would be yours

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:27.863
were you already the one you wish to be.

00:27:29.370 --> 00:27:32.043
Feeling a state produces that state.

00:27:32.900 --> 00:27:34.740
The party you play on the world stage

00:27:34.740 --> 00:27:38.130
is determined by your
conception of yourself.

00:27:38.130 --> 00:27:40.160
By feeling your wish fulfilled

00:27:40.160 --> 00:27:42.470
and quietly relaxing into sleep,

00:27:42.470 --> 00:27:45.210
you cast yourself in a star role

00:27:45.210 --> 00:27:47.800
to be played on earth tomorrow.

00:27:47.800 --> 00:27:49.740
And while asleep,

00:27:49.740 --> 00:27:53.003
you are rehearsed and
instructed in your part.

00:27:54.900 --> 00:27:56.090
The acceptance of the end

00:27:56.090 --> 00:27:59.450
automatically wills the
means of realization.

00:27:59.450 --> 00:28:01.900
Make no mistake about this.

00:28:01.900 --> 00:28:04.060
If, as you prepare for sleep,

00:28:04.060 --> 00:28:06.230
you do not consciously feel yourself

00:28:06.230 --> 00:28:08.370
into the state of the answered wish,

00:28:08.370 --> 00:28:10.630
then you will take with
you into the chamber

00:28:10.630 --> 00:28:12.470
of her who conceived you,

00:28:12.470 --> 00:28:15.030
the sum total of the
reactions and feelings

00:28:15.030 --> 00:28:16.860
of the waking day,

00:28:16.860 --> 00:28:19.860
and while asleep you will
be instructed in the manner

00:28:19.860 --> 00:28:22.470
in which they will be expressed tomorrow.

00:28:22.470 --> 00:28:25.600
You will rise believing
that you are a free agent,

00:28:25.600 --> 00:28:29.000
not realizing that every
action and event of the day

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:33.573
is predetermined by your concept
of self as you fell asleep.

00:28:34.760 --> 00:28:38.800
Your only freedom then is
your freedom of reaction.

00:28:38.800 --> 00:28:40.870
You are free to choose how you feel

00:28:40.870 --> 00:28:42.900
and react to the day's drama,

00:28:42.900 --> 00:28:45.210
but the drama, the actions, events,

00:28:45.210 --> 00:28:48.793
and circumstances of the day
have already been determined.

00:28:50.340 --> 00:28:52.630
Unless you consciously
and purposely define

00:28:52.630 --> 00:28:56.210
the attitude of mind with
which you go to sleep,

00:28:56.210 --> 00:28:59.320
you unconsciously go to sleep
in the composite attitude

00:28:59.320 --> 00:29:03.333
of mind made up of all feelings
and reactions of the day.

00:29:04.460 --> 00:29:07.380
Every reaction makes a
subconscious impression

00:29:07.380 --> 00:29:09.930
and unless counteracted by an opposite

00:29:09.930 --> 00:29:14.103
and more dominant feeling is
the cause of future action.

00:29:15.760 --> 00:29:19.160
Ideas enveloped and feeling
are creative actions.

00:29:19.160 --> 00:29:21.563
Use your divine right wisely.

00:29:22.580 --> 00:29:25.070
Through your ability to think and feel

00:29:25.070 --> 00:29:28.193
you have dominion over all creation.

00:29:29.200 --> 00:29:30.760
While you are awake,

00:29:30.760 --> 00:29:34.020
you are a gardener selecting
seed for your garden,

00:29:34.020 --> 00:29:38.030
but except a corn of wheat
fall into the ground and die,

00:29:38.030 --> 00:29:39.860
it abideth alone.

00:29:39.860 --> 00:29:42.733
But if it die it bringeth
forth much fruit.

00:29:44.240 --> 00:29:47.130
Your conception of
yourself as you fall asleep

00:29:47.130 --> 00:29:50.583
is the seed you drop into the
ground of the subconscious.

00:29:51.720 --> 00:29:54.660
Dropping off to sleep
feeling satisfied and happy

00:29:54.660 --> 00:29:58.090
compels conditions and events
to appear in your world

00:29:58.090 --> 00:30:00.813
which confirm these attitudes of mind.

00:30:02.150 --> 00:30:05.400
Sleep is the door into heaven.

00:30:05.400 --> 00:30:09.570
What you take in as a feeling
you bring out as a condition,

00:30:09.570 --> 00:30:12.830
action, or object in space.

00:30:12.830 --> 00:30:15.803
So sleep in the feeling
of the wish fulfilled.

00:30:16.980 --> 00:30:20.643
As in consciousness so on earth.

00:30:23.280 --> 00:30:24.970
Chapter three.

00:30:24.970 --> 00:30:25.803
Prayer.

00:30:27.820 --> 00:30:31.453
Prayer like sleep is also an
entrance into the subconscious.

00:30:32.630 --> 00:30:35.510
When you pray, enter into your closet,

00:30:35.510 --> 00:30:38.800
and when you have shut your
door, pray to your Father

00:30:38.800 --> 00:30:42.560
which is in secret and your
Father which is in secret

00:30:42.560 --> 00:30:44.133
shall reward you openly.

00:30:45.780 --> 00:30:47.430
Prayer is an illusion of sleep,

00:30:47.430 --> 00:30:50.520
which diminishes the
impression of the outer world

00:30:50.520 --> 00:30:52.580
and renders the mind more receptive

00:30:52.580 --> 00:30:54.143
to suggestion from within.

00:30:55.210 --> 00:30:58.410
The mind in prayer is
in a state of relaxation

00:30:58.410 --> 00:31:01.960
and receptivity akin
to the feeling attained

00:31:01.960 --> 00:31:03.893
just before dropping off to sleep.

00:31:05.180 --> 00:31:07.820
Prayer is not so much what you ask for,

00:31:07.820 --> 00:31:10.253
as how you prepare for its reception.

00:31:11.650 --> 00:31:14.370
Whatsoever things ye desire when ye pray

00:31:14.370 --> 00:31:17.963
believe that you have received
them and ye shall have them.

00:31:19.690 --> 00:31:21.090
The only condition required

00:31:21.090 --> 00:31:24.163
is that you believe that your
prayers are already realized.

00:31:25.400 --> 00:31:26.930
Your prayer must be answered

00:31:26.930 --> 00:31:29.600
if you assume the feeling
that would be yours

00:31:29.600 --> 00:31:32.700
were you already in
possession of your objective.

00:31:32.700 --> 00:31:36.420
The moment you accept the
wish as an accomplished fact,

00:31:36.420 --> 00:31:39.343
the subconscious finds
means for its realization.

00:31:40.430 --> 00:31:42.340
To pray successfully then,

00:31:42.340 --> 00:31:47.340
you must yield to the wish that
is feel the wish fulfilled.

00:31:48.950 --> 00:31:50.350
The perfectly disciplined man

00:31:50.350 --> 00:31:54.260
is always in tune with the
wish as an accomplished fact.

00:31:54.260 --> 00:31:57.940
He knows that consciousness
is the one and only reality,

00:31:57.940 --> 00:32:01.320
that ideas and feelings
are facts of consciousness

00:32:01.320 --> 00:32:04.083
and are as real as objects in space.

00:32:04.960 --> 00:32:07.080
Therefore he never entertains a feeling

00:32:07.080 --> 00:32:09.740
which does not contribute to his happiness

00:32:09.740 --> 00:32:11.260
for feelings are the causes

00:32:11.260 --> 00:32:13.713
of the actions and
circumstances of his life.

00:32:14.870 --> 00:32:17.140
On the other hand, the undisciplined man

00:32:17.140 --> 00:32:19.050
finds it difficult to believe that

00:32:19.050 --> 00:32:21.350
which is denied by the senses

00:32:21.350 --> 00:32:24.510
and usually accepts or rejects solely

00:32:24.510 --> 00:32:26.373
on appearances of the senses.

00:32:27.340 --> 00:32:28.490
Because of this tendency

00:32:28.490 --> 00:32:30.870
to rely on the evidence of the senses,

00:32:30.870 --> 00:32:34.500
it is necessary to shut them
out before starting to pray,

00:32:34.500 --> 00:32:37.773
before attempting to feel
that which they deny.

00:32:38.860 --> 00:32:41.247
Whenever you are in this state of mind,

00:32:41.247 --> 00:32:44.050
"I should like to, but I cannot,"

00:32:44.050 --> 00:32:46.480
the harder you try the less you are able

00:32:46.480 --> 00:32:49.020
to yield to the wish.

00:32:49.020 --> 00:32:51.500
You never attract that which you want

00:32:51.500 --> 00:32:55.043
but always attract that which
you are conscious of being.

00:32:56.960 --> 00:32:59.710
Prayer is the art of
assuming the feeling of being

00:32:59.710 --> 00:33:02.160
and having that which you want.

00:33:02.160 --> 00:33:05.180
When the senses confirm
the absence of your wish,

00:33:05.180 --> 00:33:09.060
all conscious effort to counteract
this suggestion is futile

00:33:09.060 --> 00:33:11.653
and tends to intensify the suggestion.

00:33:13.300 --> 00:33:15.650
Prayer is the art of yielding to the wish

00:33:15.650 --> 00:33:18.600
and not the forcing of the wish.

00:33:18.600 --> 00:33:21.370
Whenever your feeling is
in conflict with your wish,

00:33:21.370 --> 00:33:23.710
feeling will be the victor.

00:33:23.710 --> 00:33:27.360
The dominant feeling
invariably expresses itself.

00:33:27.360 --> 00:33:29.443
Prayer must be without effort.

00:33:30.470 --> 00:33:32.570
In attempting to fix an attitude of mind

00:33:32.570 --> 00:33:36.183
which is denied by the
senses, effort is fatal.

00:33:37.940 --> 00:33:41.500
To yield successfully to the
wish as an accomplished fact,

00:33:41.500 --> 00:33:44.250
you must create a passive state,

00:33:44.250 --> 00:33:47.190
a kind of reverie or meditative reflection

00:33:47.190 --> 00:33:49.713
similar to the feeling
which proceeds sleep.

00:33:50.920 --> 00:33:52.960
In such a relaxed state,

00:33:52.960 --> 00:33:55.810
the mind is turned from
the objective world

00:33:55.810 --> 00:33:59.393
and easily senses the reality
of a subjective state.

00:34:00.240 --> 00:34:02.730
It is a state in which you are conscious

00:34:02.730 --> 00:34:05.350
and quite able to move or open your eyes

00:34:05.350 --> 00:34:07.323
but have no desire to do so.

00:34:08.810 --> 00:34:10.960
An easy way to create this passive state

00:34:10.960 --> 00:34:13.913
is to relax in a comfortable
chair or on a bed.

00:34:14.890 --> 00:34:17.100
If on a bed, lie flat on your back

00:34:17.100 --> 00:34:19.450
with your head on a level with your body,

00:34:19.450 --> 00:34:22.533
close the eyes and imagine
that you are sleepy.

00:34:23.380 --> 00:34:26.750
Feel I am sleepy,

00:34:26.750 --> 00:34:27.923
so sleepy,

00:34:28.900 --> 00:34:30.683
so very sleepy.

00:34:32.400 --> 00:34:34.500
In a little while, a far away feeling

00:34:34.500 --> 00:34:38.520
accompanied by a general
lassitude and loss of all desire

00:34:38.520 --> 00:34:40.593
to move envelops you.

00:34:41.440 --> 00:34:43.930
You feel a pleasant comfortable rest

00:34:43.930 --> 00:34:46.360
and not inclined to alter your position,

00:34:46.360 --> 00:34:48.370
although under other circumstances

00:34:48.370 --> 00:34:50.283
you would not be at all comfortable.

00:34:51.320 --> 00:34:53.300
When this passive state is reached,

00:34:53.300 --> 00:34:55.950
imagine that you have realized your wish,

00:34:55.950 --> 00:35:00.740
not how it was realized, but
simply the wish fulfilled.

00:35:00.740 --> 00:35:05.400
Imagine in picture form what
you desire to achieve in life,

00:35:05.400 --> 00:35:07.993
then feel yourself as
having already achieved it.

00:35:08.940 --> 00:35:11.820
Thoughts produce tiny
little speech movements,

00:35:11.820 --> 00:35:14.130
which may be heard in the
passive state of prayer

00:35:14.130 --> 00:35:15.883
as pronouncements from without.

00:35:16.750 --> 00:35:19.000
However, this degree of passivity

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:22.930
is not essential to the
realization of your prayers.

00:35:22.930 --> 00:35:26.740
All that is necessary is
to create a passive state

00:35:26.740 --> 00:35:29.303
and feel the wish fulfilled.

00:35:30.970 --> 00:35:34.900
All you can possibly need
or desire is already yours.

00:35:34.900 --> 00:35:37.500
You need no helper to give it to you,

00:35:37.500 --> 00:35:39.700
it is yours now.

00:35:39.700 --> 00:35:41.870
Call your desires into being

00:35:41.870 --> 00:35:44.823
by imagining and feeling
your wish fulfilled.

00:35:45.760 --> 00:35:47.420
As the end is accepted,

00:35:47.420 --> 00:35:50.930
you become totally indifferent
as to possible failure

00:35:50.930 --> 00:35:54.953
for acceptance of the end
wills the means to that end.

00:35:56.410 --> 00:35:58.930
When you emerge from the moment of prayer,

00:35:58.930 --> 00:36:00.350
it is as though you were shown

00:36:00.350 --> 00:36:03.310
the happy and successful end of a play,

00:36:03.310 --> 00:36:06.433
although you were not shown
how that end was achieved.

00:36:07.340 --> 00:36:09.610
However, having witnessed the end,

00:36:09.610 --> 00:36:13.300
regardless of any anticlimactic sequence

00:36:13.300 --> 00:36:15.140
you remain calm and secure

00:36:15.140 --> 00:36:18.623
in the knowledge that the end
has been perfectly defined.

00:36:20.300 --> 00:36:22.020
Chapter four.

00:36:22.020 --> 00:36:23.413
Spirit feeling.

00:36:25.700 --> 00:36:28.990
Not by might nor by
power, but by my spirit,

00:36:28.990 --> 00:36:30.883
saith the Lord of hosts.

00:36:32.630 --> 00:36:35.120
Get into the spirit of the state desired

00:36:35.120 --> 00:36:37.410
by assuming the feeling
that would be yours

00:36:37.410 --> 00:36:39.673
were you already the one you want to be.

00:36:40.680 --> 00:36:43.580
As you capture the feeling
of the state sought,

00:36:43.580 --> 00:36:47.250
you are relieved of all
effort to make it so

00:36:47.250 --> 00:36:49.453
for it is already so.

00:36:50.390 --> 00:36:52.290
There was a definite feeling associated

00:36:52.290 --> 00:36:55.060
with every idea in the mind of man.

00:36:55.060 --> 00:36:58.430
Capture the feeling associated
with your realized wish

00:36:58.430 --> 00:37:01.180
by assuming the feeling
that would be yours

00:37:01.180 --> 00:37:04.410
were you already in possession
of the thing you desire

00:37:04.410 --> 00:37:07.183
and your wish will objectify itself.

00:37:09.140 --> 00:37:10.763
Faith is feeling.

00:37:12.340 --> 00:37:16.233
According to your faith,
feeling, be it unto you.

00:37:17.530 --> 00:37:20.300
You never attract that which you want,

00:37:20.300 --> 00:37:22.453
but always that which you are.

00:37:23.370 --> 00:37:26.380
As a man is, so does he see.

00:37:26.380 --> 00:37:29.170
To him that hath it shall be given

00:37:29.170 --> 00:37:32.523
and to him that hath not
it shall be taken away.

00:37:33.480 --> 00:37:36.640
That which you feel yourself to be you are

00:37:36.640 --> 00:37:39.173
and you are given that which you are.

00:37:40.210 --> 00:37:42.750
So assume the feeling that would be yours

00:37:42.750 --> 00:37:44.980
were you already in
possession of your wish

00:37:44.980 --> 00:37:47.263
and your wish must be realized.

00:37:48.570 --> 00:37:51.510
So God created man in his own image

00:37:51.510 --> 00:37:54.263
in the image of God created he him.

00:37:55.620 --> 00:38:00.410
Let this mind be in you which
was also in Christ Jesus,

00:38:00.410 --> 00:38:02.400
who being in the form of God,

00:38:02.400 --> 00:38:05.423
thought it not robbery
to be equal with God.

00:38:07.000 --> 00:38:09.573
You are that which you
believe yourself to be.

00:38:10.510 --> 00:38:13.320
Instead of believing in God or in Jesus,

00:38:13.320 --> 00:38:16.443
believe you are God or you are Jesus.

00:38:17.440 --> 00:38:22.030
He that believeth on me the
works that I do shall he do also

00:38:23.020 --> 00:38:28.020
should be, he that believes as
I believe the works that I do

00:38:28.200 --> 00:38:29.433
shall he do also.

00:38:30.920 --> 00:38:34.230
Jesus found it not strange
to do the works of God

00:38:34.230 --> 00:38:37.430
because he believed himself to be God.

00:38:37.430 --> 00:38:39.613
I and my Father are one.

00:38:41.210 --> 00:38:42.790
It is natural to do the works

00:38:42.790 --> 00:38:45.110
of the one you believe yourself to be.

00:38:45.110 --> 00:38:49.820
So live in the feeling of
being the one you want to be

00:38:49.820 --> 00:38:51.383
and that you shall be.

00:38:52.860 --> 00:38:56.000
When a man believes in the
value of the advice given him

00:38:56.000 --> 00:38:57.310
and applies it,

00:38:57.310 --> 00:39:02.310
he establishes within himself
the reality of success.

